These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, drawing, reading
City: san-francisco, nizza, venice, berlin
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to nizza##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
3. the person traveling to venice is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
4. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| City   | san-francisco | venice   | berlin  | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: farmhouse, palace, art-deco, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
3. the farmhouse house is the journalist##1
4. the gothic-revival house is between the farmhouse house and the palace house##2
5. the palace house is somewhere between the art-deco house and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | art-deco | palace          | gothic-revival | farmhouse     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, dog, ferret
1. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
7. the paramedic is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Pet   | rabbit    | ferret   | bird | dog    |

