.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, social-worker, engineer, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the chef is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the manager is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Job   | engineer   | social-worker         | chef   | manager    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

