.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, march, september
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in december##7
2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in may##7
4. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | december   | march | september | may    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

