.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, water, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | mirinda         | water | iced-tea |

