.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, turtle, bird
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person drinking water and the owner of the turtle##7
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
4. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
5. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Pet      | cat | turtle | bird  | hedgehog |

