.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, scientific, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, rugby, tennis
1. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching mystery movies##7
5. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching scientific movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery | scientific | martial-arts | animation     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

