.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, superhero, martial-arts
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person watching thriller movies##2
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
5. the person watching musical movies is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person watching superhero movies##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts | musical       | thriller  | superhero    |

