2. the person driving the airplane is not the person watching drama movies##6
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy | crime      | thriller   | drama  |
| Transport   | taxi    | motorbike | airplane | snowmobile |

