2. the indian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
3. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
4. the person playing go is not to the right of the japanese##8
5. the person playing domino is not to the left of the indian##8
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | dutch     | japanese | indian | german |
| Game     | billiard | go  | domino    | monopoly   |

