.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, horror, satire, mystery
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, filmmaking, puzzles, reading
1. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching satire movies is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre    | horror        | mystery | satire      | sports    |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | filmmaking | reading |

