.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
City: new-york, boston, london, edinburgh
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person traveling to boston##8
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
 9. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| City   | new-york | edinburgh  | london     | boston    |

