4. the person driving the ship is the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
7. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3     |    4    |
| Food    | onion   | eggplant    | spinach   | cabbage |
| Transport   | snowmobile | ship | roller | boat |

