.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, soccer, rowing, cricket
1. the owner of the snake is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Sport   | cycling | soccer   | cricket | rowing |

