.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, writer, coach, software-developer
1. the writer is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the coach is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the software-developer##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the firefighter##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the writer and the firefighter##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the coach is between the software-developer and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Job   | writer | software-developer      | coach     | firefighter     |

 